	<div class="banner_bg">
		<h1 class="animated bounceInLeft d-none d-md-block" style="animation-delay: 1s"> Join Disaster Alleviation Foundation</h1>
		<div class=".carousel-caption p">
			<p class="animated bounceInLeft d-none d-md-block" style="animation-delay: 2s">
				The Disaster Alleviation Foundation is not just a platform; it's a
				community of individuals who believe in the power of kindness, compassion, and solidarity.
				Together, we can make a difference in the lives of those in need and help build a more resilient world.
			</p>
